ality, and my curry chicken footlong sub was burnt at the rims also thanks to Nila. Would avoid this outlet like the plague in future and go back to the ones in Bishan and Northpoint", :time=>1665154274, :translated=>false}, {:author_name=>"Leng Leng Kwek", :author_url=>"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106206433682294881172/reviews", :language=>"en", :original_language=>"en", :profile_photo_url=>"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ALm5wu3fCgefcWz3G1RLvt63wOBRcK69mn2NZs-JEE-Y=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", :rating=>3, :relative_time_description=>"3 months ago", :text=>"Ordered a tuna 6\" but they gave me egg instead. Being overcharged.", :time=>1661253211, :translated=>false}, {:author_name=>"Corrine T", :author_url=>"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116825781304755498142/reviews", :language=>"en", :original_language=>"en", :profile_photo_url=>"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACNPEu_8SKQsUiTQ-cxm01BmDgpaQmdHUwfgDigQi_s_8A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3", :rating=>5, :relative_time_description=>"5 months ago", :text=>"I check Google time of closing at 11pm doesnâ€™t match but 1030pm last order on Saturday, lucky I came in to buy the food at the right time before 1030pm, Subway please update the timing â± to avoid disappointment from the customers. The good thing is this 3 male staff served all the way even for the few minutes before 1030pm and I appreciate lots, thank you very much!", :time=>1653800050, :translated=>false}, {:author_name=>"Nayshjin", :author_url=>"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107998343241924427011/reviews", :language=>"en", :original_language=>"en", :profile_photo_url=>"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACNPEu_fbznPbwE7iA96mGQDkrz5PIXtWRv2684YtOSOgA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3", :rating=>4, :relative_time_description=>"4 months ago", :text=>"Glad I found this subway, I can get a quick fix at a convenient location, wouldn't recommend to dine in as there isn't much space, but the staff are pretty efficient at making your sandwiches 